Package: oveRlay
Type: Package
Title: Overlay polygons for 2D point clouds
Version: 0.0.9
Author: Giuseppe D'Agostino <g.a.dagostino@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Giuseppe D'Agostino <g.a.dagostino@gmail.com>
Description: Generate polygons to annotate 2D point clouds such as scatterplots,
    UMAP, tSNE, etc. by using a square grid of user-defined resolution and 
    drawing isobands joining vertices of point-containing squares. Allows to draw
    disjointed polygons to account for outliers or disjointed clouds. Several 
    options for smoothing, clipping and offsetting the resulting sets of polygons 
    are provided.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: isoband, 
         polyclip, 
         reshape2, 
         scales, 
         splancs
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
